    <item>
      <title>当交易者权衡特朗普对俄罗斯处罚的威胁时，石油波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当市场权衡唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对俄罗斯原油的新惩罚威胁的混合言论时，石油发生了变化，如果他的对手弗拉基米尔·普京拒绝与乌克兰停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 23:20:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
